    <h1>How to Delete Your Data</h1> 
    <p>If you wish to delete your data, you can do so by following the steps below:</p> 
   <ul> 
        <li><strong>Step 1:</strong> Log in to your account.</li>
        <li><strong>Step 2:</strong> Go to Profile.</li>
        <li><strong>Step 3:</strong> Click on Delete My Account.</li> 
        <li><strong>Step 4:</strong> Select Yes if you want to permanently delete your data and lose all your data.</li> 
